      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This unit has undergone a comprehensive technical refresh, including a Beisan Systems VANOS overhaul and a precision valve clearance adjustment. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. Critically, the rear subframe has been reinforced with structural plates to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, utilizing fresh bushings and dampers to maintain the original handling profile. Finished in a concours-level exterior with a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle exhibits zero fluid seepage and optimal compression across all cylinders.",
