      "description": "Presenting a showroom-standard specimen that defies its age. This vehicle has been maintained with an obsessive level of detail, kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-finish paint protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating, free of stone chips, swirls, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the leather retains its factory-fresh aroma and supple texture, with zero bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component and switch functions with crisp, tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork, and the alloy wheels are devoid of any curb rash or pitting. This is more than a used car; it is a pristine collector-grade example that drives with the same tightness and vigor as the day it left the factory.",
